3.title: We are Recap Time Squad
3.content: This is an open-source organization where we build our projects in the public and contribute our effort to support other projects. Explore our projects Support our work . Recap Time Squad is currently operating as a home for most of Andrei Jiroh’s open-source work, although project adoption and onboarding additional maintainers are on the roadmap. We’ll be planning about setting up a legal entity (or go through a fiscal host) to make it official in the future.
